Remarks: This species has been recognised as a distinct dwarf form since its discovery in the 1980s, with strong genetic divergence noted in several more recent mtDNA studies (
McGuigan et al. 2000
;
Cook et al. 2012
;
Unmack et al. 2013
) and now supported with nuclear genetic markers.
